   git ls-remote --tags origin | grep -o 'v[0-9]\+\.[0-9]\+\.[0-9]\+' | sort -V | tail -1
   ```

#### Post-Retag Verification
1. **Verify tag on remote**:
   ```bash
   git ls-remote --tags origin | grep <version>
   ```

2. **Check tag points to correct commit**:
   ```bash
